---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import quote from "@icons/quote.svg";
---

<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="title">Why Choose Us For your Handyman Jobs</h2>
        <p class="text">
            Choosing Call Dan means choosing a local handyman who genuinely
            cares. We understand what South West Sydney residents value most and
            we always go the extra mile to ensure complete satisfaction. Our
            customers from Penrith to Campbelltown and Liverpool to Parramatta
            rely on us for consistent, quality service every time.
        </p>

        <div class="testimonial">
            <Image src={quote} alt={"handyman sydney testimonial"} />
            <blockquote>
                What sets Daniel apart from others is his readiness to assist at
                a momentâ€™s notice. He is also very efficient in his work. I
                would trust Daniel for any job that my dad used to do for or
                with me.
            </blockquote>
            <p>- Rahadian Supriatna</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    section {
        background-color: black;
        color: white;
    }
    .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    h2 {
        font-size: 1.65rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .testimonial {
        padding: 1rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--dark);
        border-radius: 6px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }
    .testimonial p {
        text-align: right;
    }
    blockquote {
        line-height: 160%;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .title {
            grid-area: title;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        .text {
            grid-area: text-content;
        }
        .testimonial {
            grid-area: testimonial;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-areas:
                "title title"
                "text-content testimonial";
        }
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        h2 {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }
    }
</style>
